Lewandoski’s Bayern Munich has now beaten Messi’s Barcelona, 8 goals to 2 in Lisbon. The match was fully dominated by the winning side. First half  of the match ended 4 – 1 and the remainder goals rolled in the second 45 minutes. Bayern Munich will now proceed to the semi-final of the Champions League to either play Man. City or Lyon. This is Barcelona’s worst defeat in the UEFA Champions League